General instructions:
-Install webserver interface "https://www.apachefriends.org/download.html"

-Download and place whole contents of this folder into xampp instalation htdocs directory.

-Start apache and Mysql modules from xampp's control panel.
-To set up the database visit "http://localhost/phpmyadmin/" on the host machine.
-Create a new database and import the existing file "biometricattendance" from this root folder.

-Visit homepage "http://localhost/Guardianweb/login.php".
